<p>The hardest part of Indian D2C marketing is feeding the content beast. Daily Instagram posts, weekly LinkedIn updates, Reels scripts, festival creatives, customer testimonials repurposed for different platforms. Predis.ai is the Bangalore-built attempt to automate this whole workflow — one prompt in, finished post out.</p>

